  "texts": [
    "A procedure called vector voting increases robustness to image artifacts or missing image data.",
    "For speedup the series is divided into blocks that are distributed to computational workers for alignment.",
    "The blocks are aligned to each other by composing transformations with decay, which achieves a global alignment without resorting to a timeconsuming global optimization.",
    "We apply our pipeline to a whole fly brain dataset, and show improved accuracy relative to prior state of the art.",
    "We also demonstrate that our pipeline scales to a cubic millimeter of mouse visual cortex."
  ],
